1.2.3
======
* Updated `magnetsdk2` to version 1.6.6

1.2.2
======
* Update to python package urllib3 (1.24.1) and requests (2.21.0)
* Update python six package from 1.10.0 to 1.11.0 to be compatible with Splunklib 1.6.5
* HTTP header 'User-Agent' defined to provide running versions information.

1.2.1
======
* Fixed wrong event timestamp parsing.
* Updated Python Splunklib package from 1.6.0 to 1.6.5.

