======
* Applied Verizon style guide.
* Changed Niddel Magnet to Verizon Autonous Threat Hunting.

1.1.0
======
* Added support for hourly alerts download.
* Updated Python dependencies.
* Updated `magnetsdk2` to version 1.6.0.